</p>
<p><b>Alleged ill-treatment by police officers and criminal investigation against a human 
rights lawyer.</b> According to the information received, there had been a lack of progress in the 
criminal investigations regarding the alleged assault against Ms. Sapiyat Magomedova, 
human rights lawyer, by officers of the Khasavyurt Police Station on 17 June 2010. However, 
the criminal investigation against Ms. Magomedova for alleged &#8220;public insult of a State 
official while on duty&#8221; continued. Ms. Magomedova was the subject of earlier 
communications (see A/HRC/16/52/Add.1, paras 181 and 183). 
