Khoshimov, born in 1969, Mr. Ma&#8217;rufa Fahriddin O&#8217;g&#8217;li Yuldoshev, born in 1990 and Mr. 
Abduazimkhodja Yakubov, born in 1982. Between 2006 and 2010, fearing prosecution in 
Uzbekistan, the above mentioned individuals fled to Kazakhstan, and upon arrival applied for 
refugee status. 
