Temmo, Mudar Al-Asimi. These individuals were reportedly detained in the Damascus 
Central Prison of Adra or Douma Prison for Women. There was no information concerning 
the situation of several other family members who were reportedly arrested in relation to the 
peaceful demonstration: Hussein Al-Labwani, Hannibal Awwad, Mahmoud Ghawrani, 
