<p>Torture <b>Alleged arbitrary detention and ill-treatment.</b> According to the information received, on 
27 January 2011, Mr. Dirar Abusisi, a Jordanian national born in 1969, left Gaza with his 
Ukrainian wife and their youngest son to move to Ukraine. On 18 February, while travelling 
by train from Kharkov to Kiev, Mr. Abusisi was reportedly approached by police officers, 
locked in one of the train&#8217;s carriages and subsequently removed from the train. He was later 
