Soon afterwards, Mr. Abusisi was allegedly put on an airplane and flown to Israel, where he 
was detained at a General Security Service interrogation center in Ashkelon. Mr. Abusisi&#8217;s 
brother reportedly tried to file a complaint with transport police about his brother&#8217;s 
disappearance, but Ukrainian police officers allegedly ignored his requests. 
