<p><b>Follow-up to communication dated 15 December 2010 (see above, case no. LKA 7/2010</b>). 
A technical assessment to establish the authenticity of the video footage which allegedly 
documents members of the Sri Lankan Army committing extrajudicial executions had been 
concluded. The overall conclusion reached by the Special Rapporteur was that the video is 
authentic and the events reflected in the video footage occurred as depicted.  
