Muayyad Salih in Mosul was raided by members of the Iraqi military, who came to arrest 
him. Mr. Ayad Muayyad Salih is a human rights defender working with the Iraqi Institution 
for Development. Shortly afterwards, Messrs. Muayyad Salih Ahmed and Ra'ed Muayyad 
